<h3 class="paragraph-P15"><a id="a__Coh√©rence_et_limites_des_instantan√©s"><span/></a><a id="snapshot-consistency-and-limitations"/><a id="__RefHeading___Toc218_3203545216"/>Coh√©rence et limites des instantan√©s</h3>
